{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 46 "The PV control in the time-domain \+
has the form" }}{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 109 "ctrl_pv_time := V[
m](t) = k[p] * ( theta[d](t) - theta[l](t) ) - k[v] * diff( theta[l](t
